# graphify — ignore machine-local internals (cache/, manifest.json, absolute-path caches,
# cost tracker, temp .graphify_* files); keep ONLY the shareable graph outputs committable.
# After `/graphify .`, `git add` graph.json / GRAPH_REPORT.md to share the graph with the team.
graphify-out/*
!graphify-out/graph.json
!graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md
!graphify-out/graph.html

# git worktrees (superpowers using-git-worktrees skill)
/.worktrees/
